zens to a free education of the kind for which they are best fitted and to the fullest extent of their powers.', 75408, 0), (485213, 'As a practising lawyer, I was mediocre, but I worked hard as a law officer of the state government and on the private side. After becoming a judge, I maintained a low profile in other activities and concentrated only on judicial work.', 67816, 0), (485214, 'There''s only two people in your life you should lie to... the police and your girlfriend.', 26129, 0), (485215, 'I''m dating a woman now who, evidently, is unaware of it.', 68460, 0), (485216, 'I don''t have a girlfriend. But I do know a woman who''d be mad at me for saying that.', 27687, 0), (485217, 'Never let a fool kiss you, or a kiss fool you.', 22256, 0), (485218, 'Save a boyfriend for a rainy day - and another, in case it doesn''t rain.', 978, 0), (485219, 'You can''t keep changing men, so you settle for changing your lipstick.', 71576, 0), (485220, 'Real magic in relationships means an absence of judgment of others.', 21729, 0), (485221, 'A kiss that is never tasted, is forever and ever wasted.', 9623, 0), (485222, 'If I''m with a man, is that going to prevent me from achieving my goal? What sacrifices will I have to make in terms of being myself, if I''m with a man? Something that young women find out really quickly is that when you start dating, all of a sudden you''re supposed to have a role. You''re not allowed to just be yourself.', 66, 0), (485223, 'I don''t date my girlfriend because she''s a model. I date her because I love her.', 70717, 0), (485224, 'My boyfriend calls me ''princess'', but I think of myself more along the lines of ''monkey'' and ''retard''.', 73850, 0), (485225, 'A bachelor''s life is no life for a single man.', 31112, 0), (485226, 'Kissing someone is pretty intimate, actually very intimate, and your heart always kind of skips a beat before you do that.', 61050, 0), (485227, 'Do not just look at your boyfriend as just a boyfriend. Look at him as a