t there. I say no to a lot of stuff that would be easy money but deviates from my meaning of life.', 4994, 0), (485773, 'Who gets the risks? The risks are given to the consumer, the unsuspecting consumer and the poor work force. And who gets the benefits? The benefits are only for the corporations, for the money makers.', 28772, 0), (485774, 'You use your money to buy privacy because during most of your life you aren''t allowed to be normal.', 148, 0), (485775, 'Profit is sweet, even if it comes from deception.', 139, 0), (485776, 'A bank is a place that will lend you money if you can prove that you don''t need it.', 13132, 0), (485777, 'The importance of money flows from it being a link between the present and the future.', 2414, 0), (485778, 'You have reached the pinnacle of success as soon as you become uninterested in money, compliments, or publicity.', 1971, 0), (485779, 'In the beginning I just wanted to survive. For the first three years, we made zero revenue. I remember many times when I was trying to pay up, the restaurant owner would say, ''Your bill was paid.'' And there would be a note saying, ''Mr. Ma, I''m your customer on the Alibaba platform. I made a lot of money, and I know you don''t, so I paid the bill.''', 66598, 0), (485780, 'Money demands that you sell, not your weakness to men''s stupidity, but your talent to their reason.', 631, 0), (485781, 'It''s not about how skinny you are or how much money or how many diamonds you have - that''s the fluff that people sometimes look at as being the main thing. It''s about understanding that the things that make you fabulous are all inside of you.', 69226, 0), (485782, 'It doesn''t take money to turn off the television and cultivate real bonding time.', 534, 0), (485783, 'Cast away care, he that loves sorrow Lengthens not a day, nor can buy tomorrow; Money is trash, and he that will spend it, Let him drink merrily, fortune will send it.', 18697, 0), (485784, 'And that''s why I wrote the book, because our 